Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,喝完的空罐請丟入回收箱裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要兩罐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我的還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣忙不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.17,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伊萬莉 可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪 老師呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,扣不上去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,給我扣住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,終於穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你們看 怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就說讓我們先過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是夢子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不過確實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 胸部稍微勒得有點緊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？ 我倒是沒感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在聊什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我要飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喝下這個 請在社團活動加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord3\1c&H00FFFF&\3c&H00FFFF&\t(0,300,0\frz360)\move(938,664,948,654,0,469)}★
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要一份微笑套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要兩罐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:16:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我要三罐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好 請不要推擠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:05.68,BackGround,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:06.92,BackGround,,0,0,0,,我也要一份微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.89,BackGround,,0,0,0,,喂 是我先來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 能給我一罐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我記得你好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我是二年…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我先把收集起來的空罐搬回社辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,OK 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,給我等一下 內卷昴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,現在在這裡跟我分個高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,又是這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,規則很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看誰最先喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,從嘴裡漏出來的話就出局了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那 準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,預備…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這個聲音是夢子老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是 終於找到個能穿上的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很有衝擊力對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直太衝擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 給我安份點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好癢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那個到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.43,BackGround,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,諸星老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,追加的70罐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝老師
