Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:20:01.14,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}將你的心 用黑白的色彩（感情）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:05.83,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}現在就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:10.05,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}在愛逐漸消失之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:17.32,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}想將我的心 毫不隱藏地 純粹地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.16,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:27.96,Insert-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}就算有些笨拙的戀心 不擅表達的愛意
